headline: CoStar Group Calls for Entries Ahead of Fifth Annual CoStar Impact Awards
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., November 05, 2025--CoStar Group (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, analytics, and 3D digital twin technology in the property markets, is accepting nominations for the fifth annual CoStar Impact Awards.
